Description_lang: When an Ancestor is called, they reduce the cooldown of $?a137040[Fire Elemental and Storm Elemental by ${$s1/-1000} sec.][Riptide by ${$s2/-1000} sec.]

description_blz.en_US: When an Ancestor is called, they reduce the cooldown of Riptide by 2 sec.
